2017
To Hell and Back
Forces TV
The story of an heroic attempt by eight Royal Marines to break the world speed marching record - a full marathon running as a troop in full fighting order, wearing combat boots and carrying 40lbs rucksack plus weapon. A moving tale of determination, courage and comradeship. (In production)


