									About							

IAC’s family of websites is one of the largest in the world, comprised of more than 150 brands and products.




Leadership

leadership
Business Management
Chris Terrill












 











Chris Terrill
CEO, HomeAdvisor









Chris Terrill is CEO of HomeAdvisor, the nation's leading website connecting consumers with screened and approved local service professionals. 
Terrill is a seasoned internet veteran, with deep experience working for consumer facing internet companies. He has worked with top tier brands, occupying either the number one or two position in their respective categories and has specialized in online subscription continuity business models. Prior to joining IAC, he served as CMO & EVP of eCommerce for Nutrisystem.com, the leader in the direct-to-consumer diet space. Prior to Nutrisystem.com he served as VP of Product and Marketing for Blockbuster.com, the online division of Blockuster Inc. Additionally, he spent 6 years with Match.com where he held several senior and VP roles, his last being VP of New Brands & Verticals, where he developed and launched new online brands, including Chemistry.com.
Terrill earned a B.S. in Advertising from The University of Texas, Austin and holds a MBA from The University of Houston. He also serves on the Board of Directors of the National Kitchen and Bath Association as well as Neat, the leading manufacturer of "digital filing cabinet" equipment and software storage.
 



